    "description": "<strong>A Top-down Horror game, where light is your only weapon against the monsters lurking in the shadows. Keep your torch alive as you attempt to uncover the secrets hidden within the forest.</strong><br><br>A night staying in a cottage, in the middle of the woods gets scary, as ominous sounds and shadowy figures appear to be coming from the woods.<br>Face your fears, and find the truth to discover why figures seem to lurk in the trees, watching you from the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/4e4f3246c1f2de6a68953476620f8def.poster.avif?t=1730111183\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/4e4f3246c1f2de6a68953476620f8def.webm?t=1730111183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore ominous locations</strong></h2>Forests, caves, swamps and more. Each with their own unique challenges to work out. Find your way through safely while avoiding a range of mysterious foes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/51397076dfcb144949683c09846196a7.poster.avif?t=1730111183\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/51397076dfcb144949683c09846196a7.webm?t=1730111183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fend off monsters</strong></h2>A variety of creatures lurk in the shadows, each with unique behaviors to work out. Keep your distance and use your torch wisely to prevent them from catching you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/622b6c650820d6b0f3fd132b8edef56a.poster.avif?t=1730111183\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/622b6c650820d6b0f3fd132b8edef56a.webm?t=1730111183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Search for clues, to understand the nightmares</strong></h2>Use your torch to help uncover hidden clues and guide you to safety. Many things aren't as they seem, and your torch can help guide you to uncover the truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/87abfac5cb2fd107948168c388ea9c83.poster.avif?t=1730111183\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076130/extras/87abfac5cb2fd107948168c388ea9c83.webm?t=1730111183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
